  "title": "Mesh Scale Fixer",
  "description": "Fixs Skeletal mesh import scale issue common with importing from blender.",
  "longDescription": "<p>Fix&#39;s Skeletal mesh import scale issue common with importing from blender, due to the scale difference of UE CM vs Blender Meters.</p><p>Also allows you to rescale your skeleton and all its mesh&#39;s while keeping a uniform root bone scale of 1.0.</p><p>If the root isn&#39;t scaled to 1.0 it can cause issues with creating and editor physics assets and becomes a hassle to deal with in animations and object bounds.</p><p><br /></p><p>Update 09-01-2023: Added 5.1 support</p>",
